## Ciphers

### ROT13
Operation: ROT13

Input: Uryyb Jbeyq

Output: Hello World

### Caesar Cipher (ROT with custom amount)

Drag **ROT13** and set the amount to any number. Try all 25 rotations using **ROT13 Brute Force**.

### XOR
Operation: XOR

Key: 0x41 (or any hex value)

Input: (your data)

### Vigenere Cipher
Operation: Vigenère Decode

Key: secretkey

Input: (ciphertext)

