## Useful Operations for CTFs

| Operation | What it does |
|-----------|-------------|
| Magic | Auto-detect encoding |
| From Base64 / To Base64 | Base64 encode/decode |
| From Hex / To Hex | Hex encode/decode |
| ROT13 | Caesar cipher with 13 rotation |
| XOR | XOR with a key |
| URL Decode | Decode URL-encoded strings |
| MD5 / SHA256 | Hash data |
| Gunzip / Inflate | Decompress data |
| From Charcode | Convert char codes to text |
| Strings | Extract printable strings |
| Entropy | Measure randomness of data |
| Parse DateTime | Decode Unix timestamps |
| JWT Decode | Decode JSON Web Tokens |
| AES Decrypt | Decrypt AES-encrypted data |

