## Saving Recipes

Click the **Save recipe** icon (floppy disk) to save your chain for later.

Share recipes as URLs — CyberChef encodes the recipe into the URL so you can send someone a working recipe link.

---

## Loading Files

You can load binary files (images, executables, zips) directly into CyberChef:

Click the **Open file** button above the Input box. 

Then use operations like:
- **Strings** to extract readable text
- **Entropy** to detect encrypted/compressed sections
- **Extract files** to unpack embedded files
- **Render Image** to display an image from bytes

