## Key Terms

| Term | Meaning |
|------|---------|
| Recipe | Chain of operations applied in sequence |
| Magic | Auto-detect and decode unknown encodings |
| Base64 | Common encoding using A-Z, a-z, 0-9, +, / |
| ROT13 | Caesar cipher shifting letters by 13 |
| XOR | Bitwise operation — common in simple encryption |
| Entropy | Measure of randomness — high entropy means encrypted/compressed |
| JWT | JSON Web Token — base64 encoded header.payload.signature |
